---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Joga" description="Terms of Service for Joga yoga and wellness platform">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-base-100 theme-transition">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 lg:py-24">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Terms of Service
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70">
          Effective Date: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
        <div class="badge badge-outline badge-lg mt-4">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">
              By accessing and using Joga ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms").
              If you disagree with any part of these terms, then you may not access the Service.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Medical Disclaimer -->
        <div class="card bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4 text-primary">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Medical & Health Disclaimer
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p><strong>Important:</strong> Joga is not a medical service and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li>Consult with a healthcare professional before beginning any yoga or fitness program</li>
                <li>Stop immediately if you experience pain, dizziness, or discomfort</li>
                <li>Our AI recommendations are not medical advice and should not replace professional medical consultation</li>
                <li>Pregnant individuals, seniors, and those with pre-existing conditions should seek medical clearance</li>
                <li>We are not liable for injuries or health issues resulting from your use of our services</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Transparency -->
        <div class="card bg-secondary/5 border border-secondary/20 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4 text-secondary">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M13 7H7v6h6V7z"></path>
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7 2a1 1 0 012 0v1h2V2a1 1 0 112 0v1h2a2 2 0 012 2v2h1a1 1 0 110 2h-1v2h1a1 1 0 110 2h-1v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v1a1 1 0 11-2 0v-1H9v1a1 1 0 11-2 0v-1H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2H2a1 1 0 110-2h1V9H2a1 1 0 010-2h1V5a2 2 0 012-2h2V2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              AI & Personalization (2025-2026 Compliance)
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p>Our service uses artificial intelligence to provide personalized yoga recommendations and progress tracking.</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li><strong>AI Transparency:</strong> You will always know when content is AI-generated or AI-curated</li>
                <li><strong>Data Processing:</strong> AI processes your workout data, preferences, and feedback to improve recommendations</li>
                <li><strong>Human Oversight:</strong> All AI-generated content is reviewed by certified yoga instructors</li>
                <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> While we strive for accuracy, AI recommendations may not always be perfect for your specific needs</li>
                <li><strong>Control:</strong> You can opt out of AI personalization and use manual class selection</li>
                <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> Your usage helps improve our AI algorithms for all users</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Services Provided</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p>Joga provides the following services:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li><strong>Live Classes:</strong> Real-time yoga instruction with certified instructors</li>
                <li><strong>Recorded Content:</strong> On-demand yoga classes and tutorials</li>
                <li><strong>AI Personalization:</strong> Customized workout recommendations based on your goals and fitness level</li>
                <li><strong>Progress Tracking:</strong> Analytics and insights about your yoga practice</li>
                <li><strong>Community Features:</strong> Forums and social interaction with other members</li>
                <li><strong>Mobile Apps:</strong> iOS and Android applications for on-the-go access</li>
                <li><strong>Virtual Reality:</strong> Immersive yoga experiences (where available)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- User Responsibilities -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">User Responsibilities</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p>As a user of Joga, you agree to:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li>Provide accurate and truthful information when creating your account</li>
                <li>Keep your login credentials secure and confidential</li>
                <li>Use the service for personal, non-commercial purposes only</li>
                <li>Respect other community members and instructors</li>
                <li>Not share, reproduce, or distribute copyrighted content</li>
                <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
                <li>Report any bugs, security issues, or violations of these terms</li>
                <li>Practice safely and within your physical limits</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Payment & Subscription -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Payment & Subscription Terms</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li><strong>Subscription Plans:</strong> We offer monthly and annual subscription options</li>
                <li><strong>Payment:</strong> All payments are processed securely through third-party payment processors</li>
                <li><strong>Auto-Renewal:</strong> Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled before the renewal date</li>
                <li><strong>Cancellation:</strong> You can cancel anytime through your account settings</li>
                <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> Refunds are handled on a case-by-case basis within 7 days of purchase</li>
                <li><strong>Price Changes:</strong> We may change pricing with 30 days notice for existing subscribers</li>
                <li><strong>Free Trials:</strong> Trial periods convert to paid subscriptions unless canceled</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Intellectual Property -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Intellectual Property</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p><strong>Our Content:</strong> All Joga content, including videos, text, graphics, and software, is protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws.</p>
              <p><strong>Your Content:</strong> You retain ownership of any content you contribute, but grant us a license to use it to improve our services.</p>
              <p><strong>Restrictions:</strong> You may not:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li>Copy, modify, or distribute our proprietary content</li>
                <li>Reverse engineer or attempt to extract source code</li>
                <li>Use our content for commercial purposes without permission</li>
                <li>Remove or modify copyright notices</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
        <div class="card bg-error/5 border border-error/20 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4 text-error">Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p><strong>Maximum Disclaimer:</strong> To the fullest extent permitted by law, Joga shall not be liable for:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li>Any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages</li>
                <li>Injuries, health issues, or medical conditions arising from your use of our services</li>
                <li>Loss of data, revenue, or business opportunities</li>
                <li>Technical issues, service interruptions, or system failures</li>
                <li>Accuracy of AI recommendations or personalized content</li>
                <li>Actions or content of third-party instructors or users</li>
              </ul>
              <p><strong>Liability Cap:</strong> Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you paid for our services in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Availability -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Service Availability & Changes</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
                <li><strong>Availability:</strong> We strive for 99.9% uptime but cannot guarantee uninterrupted service</li>
                <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Scheduled maintenance may be required with advance notice when possible</li>
                <li><strong>Service Changes:</strong> We may modify, suspend, or discontinue features with reasonable notice</li>
                <li><strong>Termination:</strong> We reserve the right to terminate accounts for violations of these terms</li>
                <li><strong>Platform Updates:</strong> Regular updates may include new features and modified functionality</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Governing Law -->
        <div class="card bg-base-200/30 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Governing Law & Disputes</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of [Your Jurisdiction], without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>
              <p><strong>Dispute Resolution:</strong> Any disputes will be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with [Arbitration Rules].</p>
              <p><strong>Class Action Waiver:</strong> You agree to resolve disputes individually and waive any right to participate in class actions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div class="card bg-success/5 border border-success/20 shadow-xl mb-8">
          <div class="card-body p-8">
            <h3 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4 text-success">Contact Information</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/80">
              <p>If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@joga.com" class="link link-primary">legal@joga.com</a></li>
                <li><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@joga.com" class="link link-primary">support@joga.com</a></li>
                <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://joga.com/contact" class="link link-primary">joga.com/contact</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Last Updated Notice -->
        <div class="text-center mt-12 p-6 bg-base-200/20 rounded-xl">
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/60">
            These Terms of Service were last updated on {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}.
            We may update these terms periodically, and continued use of our service constitutes acceptance of any changes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>